<div class="floatnone"><a href="/wiki/File:Francesco_Hayez_017.jpg" class="image" title="The Second Temple in flames"><img alt="The Second Temple in flames" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b7/Francesco_Hayez_017.jpg/250px-Francesco_Hayez_017.jpg" width="250" height="183" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b7/Francesco_Hayez_017.jpg/375px-Francesco_Hayez_017.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b7/Francesco_Hayez_017.jpg/500px-Francesco_Hayez_017.jpg 2x" data-file-width="2024" data-file-height="1480" /></a></div>
</div>
<br />
<div style="width: 250px; text-align: left; line-height: 1em"><small><a href="/wiki/Francesco_Hayez" title="Francesco Hayez">Francesco Hayez</a>, <i>The Second Temple in flames</i>, 1867. The 9th of Av, <a href="/wiki/Tisha_B%27Av" title="Tisha B'Av">Tisha B'Av</a>, is a <a href="/wiki/Ta%27anit" title="Ta'anit">fast</a> commemorating what has been called the saddest day in Jewish history,<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> which is when the <a href="/wiki/Temple_in_Jerusalem" title="Temple in Jerusalem">Holy Temple</a> was set aflame.<br />
<br /></small></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="font-size: 90%;" colspan="1">Month Number:</th>
<td>5</td>
</tr>
